text: Joanna Sternberg is an American musician based in New York City. Sternberg has released one full-length album, Then I Try Some More, on Team Love Records. The album received a 7.5 out of 10 from Pitchfork. ==Discography== Studio albums *Then I Try Some More (2019, Team Love Records) ==References== Category:Living people Category:Team Love Records artists Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
